teamcardone.name: Omowumi Adekoya
teamcardone.text: In my spare time, I enjoy reading novels.

teamcardtwo.name: Damilola Obidairo
teamcardtwo.text: I create time to intellectually debate with my family. I destress by listening to music or creating music with my voice and guitars. It gives me a lot of pleasure and satisfaction to garden and see my plants grow slowly and suddenly. In my spare time, I engage with thought-provoking books and epic/sci-fi movies.

teamcardthree.name: Dr. Seun Oladele
teamcardthree.text: Music is what I love to do. Thatâ€™s the only fun thing I know. I play video games a lot and watch movies a lot. For someone considered a researcher, I do not really like reading.

teamcardfour.name: Opeyemi Bioku
teamcardfour.text: Enjoying good music across many genres as well as movies in my leisure is my favorite thing to do.
